data.title: Mike Dunleavy: Coaching Record, Awards
data.meta_description: Checkout the Mike Dunleavy coaching record, awards, full records as a player and more on Basketball-Reference.com
data.text:
Transactions Table

June 11, 1990: Hired as Head Coach by the Los Angeles Lakers.

May 11, 1992: Traded by the Los Angeles Lakers to the Milwaukee Bucks for a 1992 2nd round draft pick (Duane Cooper was later selected) and a 1995 2nd round draft pick (Dwayne Whitfield was later selected).

May 12, 1992: Resigns as Head Coach of Los Angeles Lakers.

May 12, 1992: Hired as Head Coach by the Milwaukee Bucks.

April 26, 1996: Fired as Head Coach by the Milwaukee Bucks.
